{
  "stem": "23599.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he liked, that was one of the big stores-- you don't say stores.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, anyhow, he went there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, they wanted him to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he did-- not for money, but it was very important that you have a paper that you are working for a Germany company, that became a German company.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So when he went out for work and so the police, the Germans would come and take him and take him away.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And sometimes, you never saw them again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But this way when he had the paper from a German company, they will leave him alone because it was important that he worked for German.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know it was interesting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what they-- in the ghetto then, in the ghetto then, somehow times became kind of normal with the time, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got to used to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And became normal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was some, they are still-- they still had money, or they still money-- or they made money or somehow.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we thought there were ghettos before in-- in the Middle Ages or somewhere, we heard about ghettos.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had ghetto there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And since there were a lot of people who needed help, so what we did the community, the Jewish community there, they [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] tried to help them and collect money.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And another way of collecting money for these people was Sundays, they made teas, afternoon teas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the people who were-- people who were there-- who were there, they still worked, they they still could afford-- they would bring and make tea and coffee and would bake-- they would bake cakes and bring them a cake.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or make-- or make [NON-ENGLISH] salad, what is it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Potato salad, you know, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
